  <brief_title>Lofexidine for Opiate Withdrawal - 1</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Placebo-Controlled, Double-Blind Multi-Site Trial of Lofexidine for Opiate Withdrawal</official_title>
  <sponsors>
