  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate lofexidine for opiate withdrawal.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      An 11 day inpatient placebo-controlled, double-blind study of 96 opiate dependent, treatment
      seeking individuals randomized to 2 medication groups: lofexidine and placebo to be conducted
      in inpatient units at 3 treatment sites.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
